=1&oos=0&cnt=1&silo=25768&bucket=852508&nrank=1&crank=1&clt=R&ttype=Restaurant&tm=311335450&managed=false&capped=false&gosox=I-ADlg7wY8lqEq92hGOCPH9yxKao4fnJtoYdd5TLctoCVK2EaqcCi9rOMrUCyEbyr2E2kGrVAHAPDqusC0rt3sWqF00usVg4ZqW584remOU&cs=1838c172f2b847151494242ba9e926c18_XoT\", \"logoUrl\": \"https://static.tacdn.com/img2/branding/hotels/grubhub_05.11.2022.png\", \"provider\": \"Grubhub\", \"providerId\": \"13712\", \"providerDisplayName\": \"Grubhub\", \"headerText\": \"Get food delivered\"}]", establishmentTypes: ["Restaurants"], isClaimedIcon: "True", latitude: "40.75944", menuWebUrl: "http://www.tripadvisor.com/MobileRestaurantMenu-g60763-d459367-Westway_Diner-New_York_City_New_York.html", description: "Established in 1988, Westway Diner is a family owned and operated restaurant. Well-known as a local favorite, you will always see a familiar face enjoying the food and the atmosphere, especially the murals alongside one wall that reflect life in the \"Big Apple.\" Westway serves and delivers to all, whether they are residents of the area, business people or tourists. And with an extensive eight-page menu, everybody can be satisfied. Have a craving for a waffle at 10 PM? Don't you worry, because all the breakfast items are available at any time! And that's just the beginning, with sandwiches, salads, desserts and much more available whenever you want them. The choices are endless. What are you in the mood for?", photoCount: "985.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 41, \"count2\": 53, \"count3\": 208, \"count4\": 832, \"count5\": 1399}", email: "westwaydiner@gmail.com", website: "https://www.westwaydiner.com/", rankingPosition: "37.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"